    SOM_GeomTrainingExUniqueID
    this class is a struct that will hold the idxs of the sample array that make up a single training example The purpose of this class is to facilitate uniqueness in training examples - the hash for the object is built using all the idxs - any object that has the same idxs should come back as equal to this object
